Please add this scripts into 

authorize {  .... }

section on sites-enable file (ie. /etc/freeradius/sites-enable/default)


- URLredirectafterauth: This script allows you to set a custom page after a successful login to the captive portal
- custom_error_msg    : In this section you can customize the error message after failed authentication
- loginTime           : This script allows you to defines when user may login.(ie. after 18:00 hrs everyday, between 
                        14:00 and 15:00 hrs. etc)

